    file w p1 _tab(6) `""score": `score_attendance',"' _n
    file w p1 _tab(6) `""points": [0,1,4,6,8,10],"' _n
    file w p1 _tab(6) `""scale_marks": [20,40,60,80,90,100]"' _n
    file w p1 _tab(5) "}," _n
    
    * subsection 2.3:
